@Node "Readme3"

                                1.3 Limits
                                ==========

What I'll never do:
-------------------

I'll never build in other playroutines then the one of Soundtracker
(and Clones), because there are so many good modules for ST (I've 140; 14 Mb)
and there are enough other players playing all formats.

